{
  "stem": "734.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They were nesting, probably, somewhere in the, in the area.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And the commotion that took place because of that little ring-- it was so nice and quiet.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I mean, for miles and miles, you couldn't see a thing move, really.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we just kept following him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And eventually, we made it over-- we had to cross a railroad-- railroad tracks.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And on the other side, there was a halfway burned out house-- farmhouse and a barn.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And the policeman said to us, now, you all stay here.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Don't make a move.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Don't talk, and be quiet, and all that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And he went into the barn.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And sure enough, this is where he found the table.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "As it turned out, this couple of farmers lost everything they had in this fire that they had in this house.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "The whole roof was gone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And probably the whole interior was burnt down.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "All they had left were the walls-- left of the house and the little barn.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And they decide-- they needed a table.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this was why they decided-- it must have been easy, easy prey to just walk in and take it away, right?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they decided to take this table, which they did.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And eventually, the policeman came out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember the farmer's wife-- a woman came out, kind of very tall and skinny, crossing herself and begging him to let her go, that she, that she didn't-- how did she say-- that it was God's will.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was all God's will, that they really are-- that they really are decent people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We are very decent people, she kept on saying, crossing herself.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was all God's will.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the policeman insisted that fin-- the table was already taken apart.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
